sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Assistant Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant API as Assistant Service
    participant DB as Local Database

    User->>UI: Open assistant page (optional thread id)
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW->>API: Health check + list threads
    alt Thread id provided
        LW->>API: Get thread + thread state
        API-->>LW: Existing messages
    end
    API-->>LW: Thread list
    LW-->>UI: Render sidebar and chat history

    User->>UI: Send question
    UI->>LW: send(question)
    alt No active thread
        LW->>API: Create assistant + create thread
        API-->>LW: New thread id
        LW-->>UI: Update URL + refresh thread list
    end
    LW->>API: Stream execution for question
    loop While streaming chunks arrive
        API-->>LW: Message/tool-call chunk
        LW-->>UI: Append/stream chat bubble updates
    end
    LW-->>UI: Mark response completed

    User->>UI: Delete thread
    UI->>LW: delete()
    LW->>API: Delete thread
    API-->>LW: Deletion result
    LW-->>UI: Success toast + redirect
